commit.message:
gnu.h: Add copyright and licensing header.

2008-11-09  Thomas Schwinge  <tschwinge@gnu.org>

	* config/i386/gnu.h: Add copyright and licensing header.
	* config/gnu.h: Likewise.

From-SVN: r141721
